{"tid":2378110,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴：上上水報平安，呢排比較忙，要半工讀同全力阻撓歐中投資協定","createTime":"2021-01-24T07:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T11:10:14.000Z","uid":379267,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e954a5464d767f74391076ce65e667a3daf6fb","tid":2378110,"uid":379267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"【圖文不符的少許近況更新，當作報平安吧】<br />\n <br />\n過去一星期國際風起雲湧。個人層面也頗忙碌，除了如常的半工讀，也參加了好些閉門會議、會見外國議員、全力阻撓《歐中投資協定》等。<br />\n <br />\n▍未來也許會寫一點文章，整理思緒；希望到時候大家多多留意、分享。<br />\n <br />\n▍最後，對家醉翁之意不在酒，封區目的不是抗疫，反倒是預演未來以「區」為單位，鎮壓抗爭。<br />\n <br />\n這預示了我們的思維、動員方式也要隨著時間再進化。"},{"pid":"cc0a84464b1b888afcabeb61b12f6d6c28fb6c1c","tid":2378110,"uid":114901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"67dc6aaf8b53082646082011105012dbf33cfbaf","tid":2378110,"uid":80393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f526e6e5815ef72ed4e8bab8631b0986b9bbde","tid":2378110,"uid":379267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc0a84464b1b888afcabeb61b12f6d6c28fb6c1c","tid":2378110,"uid":114901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:53:11.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴要發攻了"},{"pid":"56d59243b491d7ba4e73a8b728188c98adcbe1b8","tid":2378110,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"同路就支持"},{"pid":"fa5e819e787df0f404643f881613c434b122ebe4","tid":2378110,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face